{"word":"τέταρτος","slug":"τέταρτος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>τέταρτος, η, ον</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:τέσσαρες\">τέσσαρες</a></el>] <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ adj.\">adj.</a> in serial sense: ‘last in a sequence of four’, <b>fourth <a href='B:470 14:25'>Mt 14:25</a>; <a href='B:480 6:48'>Mk 6:48</a>; <a href='B:510 10:30'>Ac 10:30</a>; <a href='B:730 4:7'>Rv 4:7</a>;</b> as noun in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to portion <el>ἐπὶ τὸ τέταρτον τῆς γῆς</el> over a fourth of the earth<b> <a href='B:730 6:8'>6:8</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:τεταρταῖος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:τετρα-\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}